description.narrative:
Core activities:

• Participate in a plenary session focusing on investing in Africa’s agricultural transformation, co-host a side event on Digital Harvest, and organize two breakfast panels showcasing youth livelihoods and financial inclusion partnerships;
• Provide scholarships to young entrepreneurs and Africa-based experts to attend the Forum to allow them to interact with key stakeholders within the agricultural finance sector, and coordinate their efforts;
• Contribute to the thematic working group on Finance with other leading stakeholders to review sector developments and discuss collaboration opportunities;
• Support research, publication and dissemination of the AGRF Progress Report.
